\subsection{Unlocking Test-Time Scaling}
The true potential of SDAR is realized when combining the throughput advantages from Study III with test-time scaling strategies.
As detailed in Table~\ref{tab:ar_vs_sdar_delta_transposed_subset}, applying \textbf{Majority Voting} yields substantial improvements, with gains of +11.8\% and +19.3\% on AIME benchmarks.

